多體物理（一）                          


  	讓學生深入瞭解多體交互作用及計算方法。 
1 Harmonic Oscillators and Phonons. Second Quantization for Particles  
2 Electron-Phonon Interaction. Spin Hamiltonians. 
3 Photons. Pair Distribution Function. 
4 Interaction Representation. S Matrix.  
5 Green’s Functions. Wick’s Theorem. Feynman Diagrams.  
6 Vacuum Polarization Graphs. Dyson’s Equation. Rules for Constructing Diagrams.  
7 Time-Loop S Matrix. Photon Green’s Function.  
8 Green’s Functions at Finite Temperatures. Matsubara Green’s Functions. 
9 Retarded and Advanced Green’s Functions. Dyson’s Equation.  
10 Frequency Summations. Linked Cluster Expansions.  
11 Real Time Green’s Functions. Kubo Formula for Electrical Conductivity.  
12 Other Kubo Formulas. Exchange and Correlation. 
13 Wigner Lattice and Metallic Hydrogen. Cohesive Energy of Metals.  
14 Linear Screening. Model Dielectric Functions.  
15 Properties of the Electron Gas. Sum Rules.  
16 One-Electron Properties. Electron-Phonon Interaction. 
17 Frhlich Hamiltonian. Small Polaron Theory.  
18 Heavily Doped Semiconductors. Metals.  


課程教育目標 

A. 培育具備健全品格、堅實學問、關懷社會與全球視野的人材。B. 訓練未來社會中堅及領導人才，以推動人類的永續發展。C. 培育具有科學精神與廣泛物理學知識，成為科學界中堅的人材。 
